T02D2725:93a-1: a'arya aa mo gha p'a sha panytsa de ba sto tra /
T02D2725:93a-3: 'phags pa don yod zhags pa lha lnga'i bstod pa /
T02D2725:93a-4: 'phags pa don yod zhags pa lha lnga la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2725:93b-0: sems can sdug bsngal me tshogs kyis @93b gdungs //
T02D2725:93b-1: thugs rje'i char rgyun bsil bas zhi mdzad cing //
T02D2725:93b-2: rang bzhin bde ldan gnas su 'dren mdzad pa //
T02D2725:93b-3: mgon po spyan ras gzigs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2725:93b-4: thugs rje chen po'i zhags pas 'gro kun gyi //
T02D2725:93b-5: gnod pa nges sel bde la 'god mdzad cing //
T02D2725:93b-6: sna tshogs sbrul pas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
T02D2725:93b-7: don yod zhags par grags la phyag 'tshal lo//
T02D2725:93b-8: ma chags padma'i rigs kyi sprul pa ste //
T02D2725:93b-9: klu rgyal tshul gyis gdug pa 'dul mdzad pa //
T02D2725:93b-10: dbang chen bskal pa'i me ltar rab brjid 'bar //
T02D2725:93b-11: khro rgyal rta mgrin rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2725:93b-12: chos nyid spros bral ro gcig mngon gyur tshul //
T02D2725:93b-13: ral pa gcig 'chad lha mo'i skur ston cing //
T02D2725:93b-14: bgegs tshogs 'dul phyir khro mo'i cha lugs 'dzin //
T02D2725:93b-15: ral pa gcig ma khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2725:93b-16: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yon tan gzhir gyur cing //
T02D2725:93b-17: skal ldan rjes mthun 'gro don mdzad la brtson //
T02D2725:93b-18: mgon po'i phrin las ma lus rdzogs mdzad ma //
T02D2725:93b-19: lha mo khro gnyer can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2725:93b-20: 'phags pa don yod zhags pa lha lnga'i bstod pa /
T02D2725:93b-21: pandi ta chen po ae rab tis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02D2725:93b-23: // / rgya gar gyi pandi ta don yod rdo rje dang /
